ai_summary.en: The broader crypto market is currently gripped by 'Fear,' with the BTC Fear & Greed Index at 26. Despite this, institutional 'smart money' on Ethereum shows a neutral-to-slightly bullish sentiment (0.1) with significant stablecoin inflows, hinting at accumulation or strategic holding. In contrast, the retail-driven Solana chain exhibits a slightly bearish sentiment (-0.28), marked by low volume and cautious stablecoin activity, suggesting capitulation or withdrawal from speculative plays. This divergence indicates potential resilience for ETH due to institutional positioning, while SOL may face continued short-term volatility as retail uncertainty persists.
ai_summary.zh: 加密市场目前笼罩在“恐惧”之中，比特币恐惧与贪婪指数为26。尽管如此，以太坊上的机构“聪明钱”维持中性偏看涨情绪（0.1），并伴随显著的稳定币流入，暗示着积累或战略性持有。相反，散户主导的Solana链呈现略微看跌情绪（-0.28），交易量低迷且稳定币活动谨慎，表明投机者可能正在投降或退出。这种分歧预示着以太坊因机构布局可能展现韧性，而Solana在散户不确定性持续的情况下，短期内可能面临持续波动。
